andal%20Involving%20JDS%20MP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDS%2C%20which%20has%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sha%20election%2C%20has%20refused%20to%20comment%20pending%20a%20complete%20inquiry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20senior%20party%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20-%20who%20is%20Mr%20Deve%20Gowda's%20son%20-%20said%20there%20could%20be%20no%20question%20of%20forgiving%20anyone%20who%20had%20committed%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flet-facts-come-out-hd-kumaraswamy-on-sex-scandal-involving-his-nephew-prajwal-revanna-5541796%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BLet%20Facts%20Come%20Out%26quot%3B%3A%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20On%20Nephew's%20Sex%20Scandal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20party%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Mr%20Revanna%20apparently%20fleeing%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BIf%20he%20has%20gone%20to%20a%20foreign%20country%20getting%20him%20back%20is%20their%20(the%20special%20investigative%20team)%20responsibility.%20What%20should%20I%20say...%20SIT%20will%20get%20him%2C%20don't%20worry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scandal%20broke%20last%20week%20after%20a%20woman%20filed%20a%20police%20case%20against%20Mr%20Revanna%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20sexual%20assault.%20The%20case%20was%20filed%20at%20a%20police%20station%20in%20his%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20she%20had%20been%20sexually%20abused%20multiple%20times%20between%202019%20and%202022.%20The%20clips%20circulating%20show%20more%20women%20and%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20forward%20to%20file%20cases%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20has%20also%20snowballed%20into%20a%20political%20squabble%20between%20the%20JDS%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20some%20of%20the%20national%20party's%20leaders%20distancing%20themselves%20from%20the%20state%20party%20and%20