%20Alert%20As%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%20Enter%20Key%20Stage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20campaign%20heats%20up%20for%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20weather%20department%20has%20predicted%20heatwave%20to%20severe%20heatwave%20conditions%20for%20several%20states%20over%20the%20next%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh%20temperatures%20have%20raised%20concern%2C%20as%20poll%20campaigns%20draw%20thousands%20of%20people%20under%20the%20baking%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20voters%20will%20be%20battling%20sweltering%20conditions%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20elections%20as%20heatwave%20conditions%20are%20likely%20to%20prevail%20in%20many%20states%20where%20voting%20will%20take%20place%20on%20May%207%2C%C2%A0especially%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Goa%20and%20East%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20urged%20parties%20and%20authorities%20to%20do%20more%20to%20keep%20voters%2C%20candidates%2C%20and%20polling%20station%20staff%20safe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20should%20maintain%20extreme%20caution%20during%20such%20situations%2C%20the%20authorities%20have%20said.%20There%20are%20chances%20of%20people%20suffering%20sunburn%20and%20heatstroke%2C%20the%20weather%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemperature%20in%20several%20areas%20of%20Maharashtra%20crossed%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20yesterday%2C%20with%20Solaur%20the%20hottest%20at%2043.7%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScorching%20heatwave%20gripping%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal%20has%20disrupted%20daily%20life%2C%20with%20temperatures%20soaring%20to%20alarming%20levels%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20also%20issued%20heat%20wave%20alert%20in%20Kerala's%20Kollam%2C%20Thrissur%2C%20and%20Palakkad.%20The%20heat%20wave%20conditions%20would%20prevail%20in%20many%20places%20in%20these%20districts%20today%2C%20the%20IMD%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20fear%20that%20the%20rising%20temperatures%20may%20impact%20the%20turnout%20in%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20guidelines%20issued%20by%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%2C%20people%20should%20wear%20light-coloured%2C%20loose-fitting%20clothes%20and%20cover%20the%20head%20with%20a%20cap%20or%20cloth.%20They%20should%20keep%20themselves%20covered%20and%20not%20expose%20too%20much%20of%20the%20body%20to%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlways%20carry%20plenty%20of%20fluids%20and%20water%2C%20and%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20daily%20forecast%20as%20well%20as%20advisories%20of%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20Senior%20Scientist%20at%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threshold%20for%20a%20heat%20wave%20is%20met%20when%20the%20maximum%20temperature%20of%20a%20weather%20station%20reaches%20at%20least%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20the%20plains%2C%2037%20degrees%20in%20the%20coastal%20areas%2C%20and%2030%20degrees%20in%20the%20hilly%20regions%2C%20and%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20is%20at%20least%204.5%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714375800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F61ooep4g_lok-sabha_625x300_29_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fextreme-heat-poses-a-threat-as-lok-sabha-polls-enter-key-stage-5547519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20campaign%20heats%20up%20for%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20weather%20department%20has%20predicted%20heatwave%20to%20severe%20heatwave%20conditions%20for%20several%20states%20over%20the%20next%20five%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fextreme-heat-poses-a-threat-as-lok-sabha-polls-enter-key-stage-5547519%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.a