Cp%3EA%20similar%20instance%20also%20occurred%20when%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20official%20opposition%20of%20Canada%2C%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20walked%20up%20to%20the%20stage%20to%20begin%20his%20address%20to%20the%20people%20gathered%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20people%20reached%20downtown%20Toronto%20on%20Sunday%20for%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20yearly%20gatherings%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ontario%20Sikhs%20and%20Gurdwaras%20Council%20(OSGC)%2C%20Vaisakhi%2C%20also%20called%20Khalsa%20Day%2C%20commemorates%20the%20founding%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20in%201699%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Sikh%20New%20Year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20has%20been%20organising%20an%20annual%20parade%20down%20Lake%20Shore%20Boulevard%20for%20many%20years%3B%20the%20council%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20the%20third-largest%20parade%20in%20the%20nation%20and%20that%20it%20regularly%20draws%20thousands%20of%20spectators%2C%20according%20to%20CBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20walked%20up%20to%20address%20the%20Sikh%20Community%20in%20Toronto%20loud%20pro-Khalistan%20slogans%20were%20raised%20from%20the%20crowd.%20Trudeau%20in%20a%20staunch%20assurance%20to%20the%20Sikh%20Community%20in%20the%20country%20has%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20always%20there%20to%20protect%20their%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20at%20all%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDiversity%20is%20one%20of%20Canada's%20greatest%20strengths%2C%20and%20the%20country%20is%20strong%20not%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20differences%2C%20but%20because%20of%20those%20differences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20Canada's%20greatest%20strengths%20is%20its%20diversity.%20We%20are%20strong%20not%20in%20spite%20of%20our%20differences%2C%20but%20because%20of%20our%20differences%3B%20but%20even%20as%20we%20look%20at%20these%20differences%2C%20we%20have%20to%20remember%2C%20and%20get%20reminded%20on%20days%20such%20as%20this%2C%20and%20every%20day%2C%20that%20Sikh%20values%20are%20Canadian%20values...%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20said%20during%20the%20Khalsa%20Day%20Celebrations%20on%20Sunday%20in%20Toronto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20nearly%2C%20800%2C000%20Canadians%20of%20Sikh%20heritage%20across%20this%20country%2C%20we%20will%20always%20be%20there%20to%20protect%20your%20rights%20and%20your%20freedoms%2C%20and%20we%20will%20always%20defend%20your%20community%20against%20hatred%20and%20discrimination%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20PM%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20country%20is%20enhancing%20the%20security%20and%20infrastructure%20programmes%20by%20%26quot%3Badding%20more%20security%20at%20community%20centres%20and%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20including%20Gurdwaras.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20right%20to%20practice%20your%20religion%20freely%2C%20and%20without%20intimidation%20is%20exactly%20that.%20A%20fundamental%20right%20guaranteed%20in%20the%20Canadian%20Charter%20of%20Rights%20and%20Freedoms%20that%20we%20will%20always%20stand%20up%20and%20defend%20you%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20assured%20the%20Sikh%20community%20in%20his%20Khalsa%20Day%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Trudeau's%20remarks%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20diplomatic%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20are%20going%20through%20a%20difficult%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20notably%2C%20the%20killing%20of%20India-designated%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20that%20sparked%20a%20row%20between%20India%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20was%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20in%202020%2C%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20as%20he%20came%20out%20of%20a%20Gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20June%2018%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20of%20his%20killing%20that%20reportedly%20surfaced%20in%20March%20recently%2C%20showed%20Nijjar%20being%20shot%20by%20armed%20men%20in%20what%20has%20been%20described%20as%20a%20'contract%20killing'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20killing%20led%20to%20accusations%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20had%20a%20hand%20in%20the%20killing%20--%20a%20claim%20that%20was%20denied%20by%20India%20and%20led%20to%20the%20deterioration%20of%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20Canada%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714375080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fihl75g3_justin-trudeau-_625x300_29_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpro-khalistan-slogans-raised-in-presence-of-canada-pm-justin-trudeau-on-khalsa-day-event-5547586%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20Khalsa%20Day%20Celebrations%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Toronto%2C%20loud%20chants%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20slogans%20were%20seen%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20as%20well%20as%20opposition%20leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpro-khalistan-slogans-raised-in-presence-of-canada-pm-justin-trudeau-on-khalsa-day-event-5547586%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpro-khalistan-slogans-raised-in-presence-of-canada-pm-justin-trudeau-on-khalsa-day-event-5547586%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpro-khalistan-slogans-raised-in-presence-of-canada-pm-justin-trudeau-on-khalsa-day-event-5547586%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress's%20Indore%20candida