Findia-news%2Fdelhi-chief-electoral-office-declares-paid-holiday-on-voting-day-5442052%5C%22%3Eextending%20polling%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20select%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2013%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20that%20went%20to%20the%20polls%2C%20only%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Karnataka%20recorded%20an%20increase%20in%20polling.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20states%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%2C%20such%20as%20Bihar%20(-3.5%20pp)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(-9.1%20pp)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(-7%20pp)%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20(-3.4%20pp)%20experienced%20lower%20turnouts%2C%20as%20did%20states%20with%20historically%20higher%20turnouts%20like%20West%20Bengal%20(-4.1%20pp)%20and%20Kerala%20(-6.5%20pp).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVoter%20Turnout%20%26amp%3B%20Electoral%20Results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Flok-sabha-polls-2024-low-voter-turnout-a-point-of-concern-bjp-s-gajendra-singh-shekhawat-779112%5C%22%3Ea%20higher%20voter%20turnout%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20considered%20an%20indication%20of%20change%2C%20while%20a%20low%20turnout%20suggests%20continuity.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20clear%20correlation%20or%20trend%20evident%20in%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%201951-52%20to%202019%2C%20there%20have%20been%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20In%2016%20elections%20from%201957%20to%202019%2C%20the%20turnout%20declined%20six%20times%20and%20increased%2010%20times.%20Of%20the%2010%20times%20the%20turnout%20increased%2C%20the%20incumbent%20lost%20four%20times%20and%20won%20in%20six%20elections%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%2060%25%20repetition%20rate.%20Of%20the%20six%20times%20the%20turnout%20decreased%2C%20the%20incumbent%20lost%20four%20times%20and%20won%20twice%2C%20indicating%20a%2033%25%20repetition%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Governments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20formed%20governments%20five%20times%2C%20in%201996%20(for%2013%20days)%2C%201998%20(for%2013%20months)%2C%201999%2C%202014%2C%20and%202019.%20Except%20in%201999%2C%20higher%20turnouts%20were%20seen%20in%20the%20remaining%20four%20elections.%20Thus%2C%2080%25%20of%20the%20time%20the%20BJP%20has%20formed%20governments%2C%20it%20has%20been%20following%20an%20increased%20polling%20percentage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20indicates%20that%20a%20higher%20polling%20percentage%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20BJP.%20This%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20party's%20proactive%20approach%20to%20address%20the%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20among%20voters%20after%20the%20lower%20turnout%20in%20Phase%201%2C%20a%20move%20publicly%20acknowledged%20by%20the%20BJP%20while%20other%20parties%20likely%20undertook%20similar%20assessments%20without%20public%20disclosure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20Behind%20Low%20Voting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%209%20pp%20drop%20in%20women's%20turnout%20may%20be%20attributed%20to%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan's%20absence%20from%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20where%20all%20contested%20seats%20were%20held%20by%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%20candidates%2C%20disillusionment%20among%20a%20section%20of%20supporters%20may%20stem%20from%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20fluctuating%20alliances%20and%20controversial%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20despite%20the%20Jat%20anger%20and%20farmers'%20protests%2C%20the%20shift%20of%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20seemingly%20lacks%20support%20from%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20confusion%20persists%20among%20voters%20and%20supporters%20regarding%20who%20the%20real%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20real%20NCP%20are.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20discontent%20among%20some%20BJP%20supporters%20too%2C%20it%20seems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20any%20analysis%20of%20voter%20turnout%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20multifaceted.%20Its%20impact%20on%20the%20actual%20results%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714372500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5gtls1cg_bengaluru-voters-lok-sabha-polls-2024_625x300_26_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-polls-a-look-at-lower-turnouts-first-two-phases-5547247%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20out%20of%20five%20times%20the%20BJP%20has%20formed%20governments%2C%20it%20has%20been%20following%20an%20increased%20polling%20percentage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-polls-a-look-at-lower-turnouts-first-two-phases-5547247%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20Deciphers%20Ancient%20Scrolls%2C%20Helps%20Researchers%20Find%20Plato's%20Burial%20Place%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20rapid%20strides%20made%20by%20technology%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20led%20to%20the%20proliferation%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI).%20Using%20machine%20learning%2C%20it%20analyses%20decades%20of%20data%2C%20helping%20machines%20learn%20and%20act%20in%20a%20way%20that%20requite%20human%20intelligence.%20AI%20is%20also%20helping%20humans%20decode%20complex%20problems%20and%20highlight%20history%20that%20has%20now%20been%20forgotten.%20Last%20week%2C%20University%20of%20Pisa%20in%20Italy%20announced%20that%20they%20have%20successfully%20used%20AI%20to%20decipher%20ancient%20papyrus%20scrolls%2C%20which%20revealed%20where%20the%20Greek%20philosopher%20Plato%20is%20buried.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livescience.com%2Farchaeology%2Fromans%2Fplatos-burial-place-finally-revealed-after-ai-deciphers-ancient-scroll-carbonized-in-mount-vesuvius-eruption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELive%20Science%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20papyrus%20scrolls%20were%20found%20in%20Herculaneum%2C%20a%20town%20near%20Pompeii%20that%20was%20destroyed%20when%20Mount%20Vesuvius%20erupted%20in%20AD%2079.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20they%20were%20carbonised%2C%20these%20scrolls%20were%20too%20fragile%20for%20human%20touch%20and%20required%20deciphering%20using%20hand-free%20scanning%20technology.%20This%20is%20where%20AI%20came%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20scrolls%20contained%20the%20writings%20of%20Philodemus%20of%20Gadara%2C%20a%20philosopher%20who%20studied%20in%20Athens%20and%20later%20lived%20in%20Italy.%20The%20text%20talks%20about%20Plato%2C%20the%20academy%20he%20built%20and%20his%20burial%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorians%20knew%20that%20Plato%20was%20buried%20at%20the%20academy%20he%20established%2C%20but%20they%20weren't%20sure%20about%20the%20exact%20spot.%20He%20believed%20to%20have%20died%20in%20Athens%20between%20348%20and%20347%20BC%2C%20said%20Live%20Science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20optical%20imaging%2C%20thermal%20imaging%20and%20tomography%2C%20researchers%20have%20identified%201%2C000%20words%2C%20or%20roughly%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20text%20written%20by%20Philodemus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmong%20the%20most%20important%20news%2C%20we%20read%20that%20Plato%20was%20buried%20in%20the%20garden%20reserved%20for%20him%20(a%20private%20area%20intended%20for%20the%20Platonic%20school)%20of%20the%20Academy%20in%20Athens%2C%20near%20the%20so-called%20Museion%20or%20sacellum%20sacred%20to%20the%20Muses.%20Until%20now%20it%20was%20only%20known%20that%20he%20was%20buried%20generically%20in%20the%20Academy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20that%20researchers%20have%20used%20AI%20to%20read%20ancient%20scrolls%20that%20survived%20Mount%20Vesuvius's%20eruption.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20researchers%20deciphered%20a%20different%20scroll%20that%20was%20charred%20during%20the%20volcanic%20eruption%20at%20a%20nearby%20villa%20that%20once%20belonged%20to%20Julius%20Caesar's%20father-in-law.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714372500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fd5b010kg_plato-statue-pexels_625x300_29_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fai-deciphers-ancient-scrolls-helps-researchers-find-out-where-plato-is-buried-5547285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Using%20optical%20imaging%2C%20thermal%20imaging%20and%20tomography%2C%20researchers%20have%20identified%201%2C000%20words%2C%20or%20roughly%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20text%20written%20by%20Philodemus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fai-deciphers-ancient-scrolls-helps-researchers-find-out-where-plato-is-buried-5547285%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fai-deciphers-ancient-scrolls-helps-researchers-find-out-where-plato-is-buried-5547285%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fai-deciphers-ancient-scrolls-helps-researchers-find-out-where-plato-is-buried-5547285%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PlayStation%205%20Slim%3A%20Sony%20announces%20'limited%20period%20offer'%20on%20gaming%20console%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714372344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F11%2Ffull%2F1697008191-1052.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2