%20country's%20highest%20organ%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYang%20Xiaoming%2C%2062%2C%20was%20booted%20on%20April%2023%20from%20the%20National%20People's%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20serious%20discipline%20and%20law%20violations%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fa%2F202404%2F28%2FWS662de46fa31082fc043c4714.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estate%20media%20reported%20this%20weekend%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20phrase%20typically%20means%20a%20person%20is%20under%20investigation%20for%20corruption%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20Yang%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20Sinopharm's%20vaccine%20subsidiary%20China%20National%20Biotec%20Group%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20one%20of%20the%20nearly%203%2C000%20congressional%20deputies%20who%20make%20decisions%20on%20major%20national%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npc.gov.cn%2Fnpc%2Fc2%2Fc30834%2F202404%2Ft20240426_436820.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20congressional%20report%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20his%20dismissal%20said%20he%20served%20on%20the%20Ethnic%20Affairs%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYang%20is%20a%20medical%20researcher%20who%20led%20the%20Sinopharm%20team%20that%20developed%20the%20BBIBP-CorV%20vaccine%2C%20a%20COVID-19%20shot%20that%20was%20the%20nation's%20first%20approved%20for%20general%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnown%20colloquially%20as%20the%20Sinopharm%20vaccine%2C%20the%20shot%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20widely%20administered%20COVID-19%20shots%20in%20China%2C%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Ffeature-stories%2Fdetail%2Fthe-sinopharm-covid-19-vaccine-what-you-need-to-know%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eefficacy%20of%2079%25%20against%20hospitalization%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20developing%20the%20Sinopharm%20shot%2C%20Yang%20was%20also%20the%20head%20of%20China's%20vaccine%20project%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.most.gov.cn%2Fprogrammes1%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E863%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20Beijing's%20push%20to%20make%20the%20country%20more%20independent%20by%20developing%20homegrown%20advanced%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYang's%20dismissal%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20Weibo%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20X%2C%20with%20thousands%20of%20posts%20questioning%20the%20circumstances%20behind%20his%20removal%20from%20deputy%20status.%20It%20received%20around%20180%20million%20views%20and%2C%20for%20several%20hours%2C%20was%20the%20platform's%20hottest%20topic%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20soon%20morphed%20into%20wild%20speculation%20that%20the%20reason%20behind%20his%20dismissal%20may%20have%20been%20related%20to%20the%20Sinopharm%20vaccine%2C%20though%20there%20has%20been%20no%20evidence%20to%20indicate%20as%20such.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20father%20of%20the%20Sinopharm%20vaccine%20violated%20regulations%20and%20laws%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20there%20are%20problems%20with%20the%20vaccines%20he%20developed%20and%20produced%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F2495784474%2FObLkWbbkr%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20%26quot%3BDr%20Chen%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20popular%20medical%20blogger%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20wait%20before%20panicking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20about%20Yang%20comes%20amid%20China's%20sweeping%20crackdown%20on%20corruption%20in%20its%20healthcare%20sector%2C%20with%20investigations%20launched%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.china.com.cn%2Findustry%2Fmedicine%2F20230731%2F6015527.shtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20hospital%20deans%20and%20secretaries.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20the%20heaviest%20disciplinary%20campaign%20ever%20enforced%20on%20China's%20healthcare%20industry%2C%20plagued%20for%20years%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fheapol%2Farticle%2F3