quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20openly%20acknowledged%20it%20cannot%20correct%20inaccurate%20information%20produced%20by%20its%20generative%20AI%20tool%20and%20has%20failed%20to%20explain%20where%20the%20data%20comes%20from%20and%20what%20ChatGPT%20stores%20about%20individuals%2C%20said%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20errors%20are%20unacceptable%20for%20information%20about%20individuals%20because%20EU%20law%20stipulates%20that%20personal%20data%20must%20be%20accurate%2C%20NOYB%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20system%20cannot%20produce%20accurate%20and%20transparent%20results%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20used%20to%20generate%20data%20about%20individuals%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Maartje%20de%20Graaf%2C%20data-protection%20lawyer%20at%20NOYB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20technology%20has%20to%20follow%20the%20legal%20requirements%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20%26quot%3Brepeatedly%20provided%20incorrect%20information%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20birth%20date%20of%20NOYB%20founder%20Max%20Schrems%20%26quot%3Binstead%20of%20telling%20users%20that%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20necessary%20data%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20refused%20Schrems's%20request%20to%20rectify%20or%20erase%20the%20data%20despite%20it%20being%20incorrect%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20impossible%2C%20NOYB%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20to%20adequately%20respond%26quot%3B%20to%20his%20request%20to%20access%20his%20personal%20data%2C%20again%20in%20violation%20of%20EU%20law%2C%20said%20NOYB%2C%20and%20the%20firm%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20not%20even%20pretend%20that%20it%20can%20comply%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign%20group%2C%20which%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20tech%20giants%20since%20its%20creation%20in%202018%2C%20said%20it%20was%20asking%20Austria's%20data%20protection%20authority%20to%20investigate%20and%20fine%20OpenAI%20to%20bring%20it%20in%20line%20with%20EU%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBursting%20onto%20the%20scene%20in%20November%202022%2C%20ChatGPT%20sparked%20a%20frenzy%20among%20tech%20users%20dazzled%20by%20its%20ability%20to%20reel%20off%20dissertations%2C%20poems%20or%20translations%20in%20mere%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20criticism%20of%20the%20technology%20has%20since%20prompted%20legal%20action%20in%20some%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EItaly%20temporarily%20blocked%20the%20programme%20in%20March%202023%2C%20while%20France's%20regulatory%20authority%20began%20an%20investigation%20after%20a%20series%20of%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20European%20working%20group%20has%20also%20been%20set%20up%20to%20improve%20coordination%2C%20although%20NOYB%20remains%20sceptical%20about%20the%20authorities'%20efforts%20to%20regulate%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714368120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F59i22pfg_chatgpt-_625x300_29_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchatgpt-keeps-hallucinating-openais-ai-tool-faces-austria-complaint-5546914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Vienna-based%20privacy%20campaign%20group%20said%20Monday%20it%20would%20file%20a%20complaint%20against%20ChatGPT%20in%20Austria%2C%20claiming%20the%20%26quot%3Bhallucinating%26quot%3B%20flagship%20AI%20tool%20invents%20wrong%20answers%2C%20which%20creator%20OpenAI%20cannot%20correct.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchatgpt-keeps-hallucinating-openais-ai-tool-faces-austria-complaint-5546914%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchatgpt-keeps