0it's%20a%20storm.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20win%20all%2029%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Congress%20chief%20Arvinder%20Singh%20Lovely%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20on%20April%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Delhi%20Congress%20Unit%20was%20against%20an%20alliance%20with%20a%20party%20which%20was%20formed%20on%20the%20sole%20basis%20of%20leveling%20false%2C%20fabricated%2C%20and%20malafide%20corruption%20charges%20against%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Despite%20that%2C%20the%20party%20made%20a%20decision%20to%20ally%20with%20the%20AAP%20in%20Delhi...%2C%26quot%3B%20Arvinder%20Singh%20Lovely%20wrote%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lovely%20was%20appointed%20to%20the%20post%20in%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20Congress%20National%20President%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Mr%20Lovely%20said%20that%20all%20unanimous%20decisions%20taken%20by%20the%20Senior%20Delhi%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20been%20unilaterally%20vetoed%20by%20the%20AICC%20General%20Secretary%20(Delhi%20In-charge).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20my%20appointment%20as%20DPCC%20President%2C%20the%20AICC%20General%20Secretary%20(Delhi%20In-charge)%20has%20not%20allowed%20me%20to%20make%20any%20senior%20appointments%20in%20the%20DPCC.%20My%20request%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20veteran%20leader%20as%20Media%20head%20of%20DPCC%20was%20blatantly%20rejected.%20To%20date%2C%20the%20AICC%20General%20Secretary%20(Delhi%20In-charge)%20has%20not%20allowed%20the%20DPCC%20to%20appoint%20all%20Block%20presidents%20in%20the%20city.%20Resultantly%20more%20than%20150%20blocks%20in%20Delhi%20do%20not%20presently%20have%20a%20Block%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorena%20and%20Gwalior%20will%20vote%20on%20May%207%20in%20the%20Phase%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20for%20the%20Gwalior%20and%20Morena%20Lok%20Sabha%20Constituencies%20in%20Madh