0Aquilino%20urged%20China's%20neighbors%20to%20be%20vocal%20about%20Beijing's%20aggression.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Indo-Pacific%20Command's%20outgoing%20chief%20said%20China%20has%20been%20turning%20up%20the%20heat%20on%20its%20neighbors%20with%20progressively%20bolder%20military%20actions%20in%20a%20pattern%20designed%20to%20catch%20them%20off%20guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdm.%20John%20Aquilino%20described%20Beijing's%20strategy%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Ff926f540-d5c2-43f2-bd8f-c83c0d52bcda%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bboiling%20frog%26quot%3B%20tactic%2C%20or%20to%20gradually%20step%20up%20aggression%20so%20that%20other%20nations%20don't%20immediately%20realize%20when%20a%20critical%20point%20in%20conflict%20is%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20published%20on%20Sunday%2C%20he%20told%20the%20FT%20that%20these%20nations%20must%20speak%20up%20and%20call%20out%20aggressive%20behavior%20from%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20continual%20description%20of%20China's%20bad%20behavior%20that%20is%20outside%20legal%20international%20norms.%20And%20that%20story%20has%20to%20be%20told%20by%20all%20the%20nations%20in%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAquilino%2C%20who%20led%20US%20forces%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20for%20three%20years%2C%20cited%20two%20major%20conflict%20points%20involving%20China%20%E2%80%94%20Taiwan%20and%20the%20Second%20Thomas%20Shoal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20continually%20been%20posturing%20more%20aggressively%20toward%20Taiwan%2C%20which%20it%20claims%20as%20its%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20leaders%20are%20shifting%20to%20more%20war-like%20rhetoric%20against%20the%20self-governed%20island%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaiwan-deploys-fighter-jets-ships-10-china-warplanes-fly-airspace-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_b