ord-losses-fraud-federal-trade-commission-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20whopping%20%241.3%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Americans%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernard%20Kim%2C%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmtch-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatch%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spoke%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fmatch-group-ceo-bernard-kim-on-romance-scams%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20growing%20threat%20of%20online%20romance%20scams%20carried%20out%20by%20people%20overseas.%20Match%20Group%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-match-group-history-of-tinder-parent-company-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20owns%20Match.com%20and%20Tinder%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20largest%20online%20dating%20company%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20things%20happen%20in%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20told%20CBS%20when%20asked%20what%20he%20would%20tell%20customers%20who%20have%20fallen%20victim%20to%20scams.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20really%20difficult.%20I%20have%20a%20tremendous%20amount%20of%20empathy%20for%20things%20that%20happen%2C%20but%20I%20mean%2C%20our%20job%20is%20to%20keep%20people%20safe%20on%20our%20platforms%3B%20that%20is%20top%20foremost%2C%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FTC%20filed%20a%20federal%20lawsuit%20against%20Match%20Group%20in%20July%202022%2C%20alleging%20that%20%26quot%3Bas%20many%20as%2025-30%20percent%20of%20Match.com%20members%20who%20registered%20each%20day%20were%20using%20Match.com%20to%20perpetrate%20scams%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Match%20Group%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20figures%20mentioned%20in%20the%20claim%20are%20misleading%20and%20that%20the%20court%20dismissed%20claims%20related%20to%20the%20number%20of%20sign-ups%20that%20may%20be%20related%20to%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20Match%20is%20working%20with%20law%20enforcement%20to%20combat%20scams%20and%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%26quot%3B%20companies%20in%20the%20space%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20done%20several%20romance%20scam%20prevention%20campaigns%2C%26quot%3B%20Match%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20done%20some%20pop-up%20messages%20within%20our%20apps%2C%20educating%20people%20on%20the%20common%20behaviors%20of%20scams%20and%20then%20also%20how%20to%20avoid%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScams%20carried%20out%20on%20Match%20included%20%26quot%3Bphishing%26quot%3B%20to%20steal%20consumers'%20personal%20information%20and%20%26quot%3Bsextortion%20scams%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20scammers%20trick%20a%20victim%20into%20sending%20compromising%20videos%20or%20pictures%20that%20they%20then%20use%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-soldier-romance-scam-fort-bragg-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextort%20money%20from%20the%20victim%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20FTC%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20authorities%2C%20retrieving%20stolen%20money%20after%20it's%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20scammers%20is%20extremely%20difficult%2C%20and%20victims%20typically%20do%20not%20recoup%20all%20of%20the%20money%20they%20lose%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolk%20County%20Sheriff%20Grady%20Judd%20in%20Florida%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscammers-trick-woman-publishers-clearinghouse-sweepstakes-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthorities%20could%20only%20recover%20around%20%2440%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20thieves%20convinced%20a%20woman%20she%20had%20won%20a%20fake%20Publisher's%20Clearing%20House%20sweepstakes.%20The%20thieves%20stole%20more%20than%20%24400%2C000%20from%20her.%3C%2