https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmorning-routine-longevity-expert-david-sinclair-reversed-biological-age-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifestyle%20tips%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20earned%20his%20share%20of%20critics%20who%20say%20his%20research%20isn't%20always%20backed%20up%20by%20sufficient%20evidence.%20But%20over%20the%20past%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fhealth%2Fwellness%2Fdavid-sinclair-longevity-aging-criticism-645fddc5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Sinclair%20has%20been%20battling%20a%20new%20level%20of%20backlash%20from%20colleagues%20and%20researchers%20who%20say%20his%20claims%20on%20curing%20aging%20have%20gone%20too%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20matter%20of%20semantics%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20began%20on%20February%2029%2C%20when%20Sinclair's%20dog-supplement%20company%2C%20Animal%20Biosciences%2C%20issued%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20proud%20of%20the%20teams%20at%20NCSU%20and%20Animal%20Biosciences%2C%20who%2C%20after%20years%20of%20collaborative%20research%20and%20a%20clinical%20trial%2C%20have%20developed%20the%20first%20supplement%20proven%20to%20reverse%20aging%20in%20dogs%2C%26quot%3B%20Sinclair%20said%20in%20the%20release%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fnew-supplement-reverses-aging-dogs-study-1874899%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAnimal%2520Biosciences%252C%2520Inc.%252C%2520based%2Cdogs%252C%2522%2520the%2520release%2520said.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Newsweek%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESinclair%20contends%20that%20he%20was%20misquoted.%20%26quot%3BThe%20actual%20quote%20that%20I%20had%20approved%20was%20'proven%20to%20reverse%20the%20effects%20of%20aging%20in%20dogs%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20Journal%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20this%20was%20a%20reasonable%20statement.%26quot%3B%