rted%20based%20on%20an%20email%20circulated%20by%20the%20Academy.%20Barzilai%20has%20since%20taken%20over%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Sinclair%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnimal%20Biosciences%20reissued%20a%20press%20release%20walking%20back%20the%20%26quot%3Breverse%20aging%26quot%3B%20claim.%20But%20scientists%20in%20the%20field%20say%20the%20issue%20is%20even%20more%20fundamental%3A%20There's%20no%20way%20to%20reverse%20aging%2C%20much%20less%20measure%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forgan-age-wsj-study-nature-biological-age-longevity-bryan-johnson-2024-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBiological%2520age%2520has%2520become%2520a%2Cthe%2520National%2520Institute%2520on%2520Aging.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Econcept%20of%20biological%20age%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20true%20age%20that%20our%20cells%2C%20tissues%2C%20and%20organ%20systems%20appear%20to%20be%2C%20based%20on%20biochemistry%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Institute%20on%20Aging%20%E2%80%94%20is%20gaining%20traction%20in%20longevity%20circles.%20Yet%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20fuzzy%20and%20controversial%20concept%20because%20there's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-maximum-age-of-humans-115-or-older-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eno%20standard%20for%20normal%20aging%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20way%20we%20age%20varies%20a%20lot%20from%20person%20to%20person.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20working%20to%20standardize%20longevity%20medicine%20say%20it%20could%20take%20years%20before%20it'll%20be%20recognized%20as%20an%20official%20field%20like%20cardiology%20or%20neurology%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.technologyreview.com%2F2024%2F03%2F18%2F1089888%2Fthe-quest-to-legitimize-longevity-medicine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20MIT%20Technology%20Review%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20new%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrea%20Maier%20of%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%20and%20cofounder%20of%20the%20private%20%26quot%3Bhigh-end%26quot%3B%20Chi%20Longevity%20clinic%20told%20MIT%20Technology%20Review.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20organize%20ourselves%3B%20we%20have%20to%20set%20standards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20billions%20of%20dollars%20are%20being%20funneled%20into%20research.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-investing-longevity-biotech-vc-billionaires-2024-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThey%2527re%2520in%2520good%2520company%2Caging%2520at%2520the%2520cellular%2520level.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELongevity%20startups%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20drew%20a%20global%20investment%20of%20more%20than%20%245.2%20billion%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%20And%20those%20backed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frichest-wealthiest-entrepreneurs-ceo-billionaires-tech-searching-hacking-longevity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eworld's%20wealthiest%20executives%20like%20Jeff%20Bezos%20and%20Peter%20Thiel%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20dedicated%20to%20studying%20cellular%20aging%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20cures.%20That%20means%20debates%20about%20the%20semantics%20of%20aging%20will%20only%20become%20more%20relevant%20to%20our%20daily%20lives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freverse-aging-david-sinclair-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714340617000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662ea5ea0dfb1341e900143e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freverse-aging-david-sinclair-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr.%20David%20Sinclair%20is%20at%20the%20center%20of%20a%20