O%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mygoldadvisor.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMy%20Gold%20Advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20that's%20the%20wrong%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20will%20just%20go%20buy%20gold%20from%20Costco%2C%20even%20though%20they%20don't%20know%20why%20they're%20buying%20it%2C%20or%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuff%20shared%20his%20top%20three%20tips%20that%20shoppers%20should%20remember%20when%20buying%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1%3A%20Gold%20is%20for%20saving%2C%20not%20quick%20profit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20buy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-invest-in-gold%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephysical%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20flip%20a%20profit.%20You%20buy%20physical%20gold%20to%20store%20wealth%20and%20to%20protect%20what%20you've%20earned%2C%26quot%3B%20Huff%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20trading%20out%20your%20dollars%20for%20a%20physical%20asset%20outside%20of%20the%20banking%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20appreciates%20at%20around%208%25%20per%20year%20on%20average%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprivatebank.jpmorgan.com%2Fnam%2Fen%2Finsights%2Fmarkets-and-investing%2Fis-it-a-golden-era-for-gold%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20popular%20among%20those%20seeking%20a%20hedge%20against%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20also%20means%20buyers%20should%20plan%20to%20hold%20onto%20any%20physical%20gold%20they%20buy%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20one%20year%2C%20and%20preferably%20much%20longer.%20Huff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20increase%20of%208%25%20would%20also%20help%20cover%20any%20discounts%20or%20expenses%20necessary%20to%20sell%20the%20gold%20for%20cash%20since%20dealers%20don't%20always%20pay%20spot%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2%3A%20Start%20researching%20dealers%20early%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20waiting%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-price-forecast-outlook-spot-fed-interest-rate-cut-rosenberg-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egold%20to%20appreciate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Huff%20recommends%20researching%20and%20connecting%20with%20reputable%20dealers%20who%20would%20buy%20the%20bars%20at%20a%20fair%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20be%20especially%20helpful%20if%20circumstances%20require%20an%20earlier-than-planned%20selling%20of%20the%20gold%20stash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20the%20time%20comes%2C%20you%20already%20have%20that%20in%20your%20back%20pocket.%20You've%20already%20vetted%20them%20out%20and%20know%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20Huff%20said%20silver%20makes%20a%20nice%20complement%20to%20gold%20for%20a%20for%20a%20simple%20investing%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20ratio%20that%20we%20watch%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-buy-silver%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egold%20to%20silver%3C%2Fa%3E%20ratio%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20gold%20becomes%20cheaper%20relative%20to%20silver%2C%20you%20could%20sell%20some%20of%20your%20silver%20or%20trade%20some%20of%20your%20silver%20for%20gold%20and%20flip-flop%20your%20portfolio%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3%3A%20Keep%20it%20safe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20silver%20can%20take%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space%2C%20Huff%20said%20gold%20is%20surprisingly%20compact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20fit%20a%20million%20dollars%20worth%20of%20gold%20in%20two%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20secure%20smaller%20stashes%2C%20Huff%20said%20a%20small%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-home-safe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efireproof%20safe%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20preferably%20bolted%20to%20the%20floor%20%E2%80%94%20is%20likely%20sufficient.%20A%20fully%20insured%20self-storage%20unit%20is%20also%20a%20reasonable%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarger%20holdings%20can%20be%20kept%20at%20private%20depositories%20that%20specialize%20in%20precious%20metals%20and%20collectibles%20and%20include%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20approach%20should%20be%20that%20you%20never%20want%20to%20sell%20it.%20You%20never%20want%20to%20spend%20your%20savings%2C%20and%20gold%20should%20be%20approached%20that%20same%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Huff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-things-costco-shoppers-should-know-before-buying-gold-bars-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714336532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662c55fb10dfcda409642a0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-things-costco-shoppers-should-know-before-buying-gold-bars-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Costco%20sells%20an%20estimated%20%24200%20million%20worth%20of%20gold%20and%20silver%20bars%20per%20month%2C%20but%20shoppers%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20some%20key%20things%20before%20buying.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40businessinsider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A84%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-things-costco-shoppers-should-know-before-buying-gold-bars-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Williams-Sonoma%20to%20pay%20%243.1%20million%20after%20FTC%20sued%20it%2C%20saying%20it%20falsely%20labeled%20products%20as%20'Made%20in%20USA'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Williams-Sonoma%20sign.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662e74e10dfb1341