atch%20had%20fetched%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20house%20record.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watch%20had%20belonged%20to%20John%20Jacob%20Astor%20IV%2C%20a%20businessman%20and%20real%20estate%20developer%20who%20went%20down%20with%20the%20ship%20when%20it%20sank%20in%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%20in%201912.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAstor%20is%20well%20known%20as%20the%20richest%20passenger%20aboard%20the%20R.M.S.%20Titanic%20and%20was%20thought%20to%20be%20among%20the%20richest%20people%20in%20the%20world%20at%20that%20time%2C%20with%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20roughly%20%2487%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20Henry%20Aldridge%20%26amp%3B%20Son%20says%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbid.henryaldridge.com%2Fauctions%2F8886%2Fhenry-10054%2Flot-details%2F21a9a7ea-fb02-418b-b4fa-b14300fc55de%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAstor%20IV%2C%20who%20was%2047%20at%20the%20time%20the%20Titanic%20sank%2C%20helped%20his%20wife%2C%20Madeleine%2C%20onto%20a%20lifeboat%20and%20then%20smoked%20a%20last%20cigarette%20as%20the%20ship%20went%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2014-carat%20gold%20Waltham%20pocket%20watch%2C%20engraved%20JJA%2C%20was%20found%20on%20his%20body%20when%20it%20was%20recovered%20a%20week%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20highest%20amount%20previously%20paid%20for%20a%20Titanic%20artifact%20had%20been%20%C2%A31.1%20million%2C%20or%20roughly%20%241.4%20million%2C%20for%20a%20violin%20that%20band%20member%20Wallace%20Hartley%20apparently%20played%20to%20try%20to%20calm%20passengers%20as%20the%20ship%20went%20under.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20for%20the%20violin%20was%20sold%20at%20the%20same%20auction%20on%20Saturday%20for%20%C2%A3360%2C000%2C%20which%20is%20about%20%24455%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225995%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20RMS%20Titanic.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64951a1e65b9ce0018a484ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223619%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%