%20than%2012%20varieties%20of%20flowers%20in%20his%2052-acre%20farmland.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20other%20difficulties%20that%20he%20faced%20while%20setting%20up%20the%20farm%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarming%20does%20come%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20risks%2C%20especially%20with%20changes%20in%20climate%20conditions.%20As%20a%20young%20man%20in%20the%20business%2C%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20garner%20the%20trust%20of%20investors%20and%20banks.%20Once%20that%20was%20done%2C%20things%20became%20easier.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrikanth%20grows%2012%20varieties%20of%20flowers%20in%20his%2052-acre%20farmland.%20These%20flowers%20include%20Roses%2C%20Gerbera%2C%20Carnations%2C%20Gypsophila%20among%20others%20that%20are%20grown%20organically%20in%20greenhouses%20and%20polyhouses.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20try%20to%20be%20as%20organic%20and%20sustainable%20as%20possible%20while%20cultivating%20our%20flowers.%20All%20the%20waste%20that%20is%20produced%20once%20the%20flowers%20are%20ready%20to%20be%20shipped%20is%20used%20to%20make%20vermicompost%20which%20is%20in%20turn%20used%20to%20fertilise%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20the%20industry%20for%20decades%2C%20Srikanth%20has%20learned%20a%20few%20lessons%20that%20he%20carries%20and%20shares%20with%20everyone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20general%20trend%20in%20the%20society%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20youth%2C%20to%20not%20become%20farmers.%20This%20is%20mostly%20because%20of%20the%20idea%20that%20there%20are%20no%20profits.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20play%20your%20cards%20right%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20be%20made%20in%20this%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20all%20those%20who%20are%20wanting%20to%20enter%20the%20industry%2C%20it%20is%20a%20great%20time%20to%20be%20here.%20However%2C%20if